formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. As informed by the promoter, a project alteration application has been initiated by the promoter on 03-06-2022 whereby the promoter seeks to de-register Building/ Wing Number A1 of the project as the promoter does not intend to construct Building / Wing Number A1 of the project. The said application is pending to be approved by the GujRERA authority as on 30-06-2022. Therefore, the above certificate is being issued as per the project specifications as they stood before making the said application. As informed by the promoter, Form 1 and Form 2 are issued by the respective persons as per the project specifications stated in the said alteration application. 

2. In Form No. 2 issued for the period ending on 20-06-2022, the total estimated cost of construction has been stated as Rs. 17,05,00,000/- since as mentioned in note no. 1 above the said form has been issued after considering the project specifications made in the said alteration application. 

3. The total estimated cost of construction has been revised at Rs. 19,10,00,000/- as per quarter compliance Form No. 2 issued by the project engineer for the period ending on 20-03-2022.  However, as informed by him and promoter of the project, there are no provisions/ utilities available on the website of GujRera to make such changes/ revisions online and hence the figure of estimated total cost as per engineer's certificate is being auto populated in Form No. 3 at column No. 1 (ii) a(i) and is still appearing at old estimates of engineer only. 

4. Similarly, as informed by the promoter, there are no further sum payable for obtaining development rights, FSI, additional FSI, fungible area and any other incentive under DCR from Local Authority or State Government or any Statutory Authority as per column No. 1 (i)(b) and accordingly estimated cost and the cost incurred and paid towards the said expense would be same i.e. Rs. 16,53,950/-.

5. The sub-total of estimated land cost would be Rs. 2,94,21,550/-. 

6. The estimated payment of taxes, cess, fees, etc. to any Statutory Authority (as per column no. 1 (ii) (b)) is Rs. 52,000/-.

7. The sub-total of estimated development cost is Rs. 19,29,60,000/- and the sub-total of incurred and paid development cost is Rs.15,58,17,319/-.

8. Therefore, Net Amount which can be withdrawn from the Designated Bank Account under this certificate is Rs. 26,45,488/- instead of Rs. -4,30,83,831/-.

9. The estimated Balance Cost to Complete the Real Estate Project (Difference of Total Estimated Project cost less Cost incurred) is Rs. 3,71,42,681/-.
